svg.title: Buggie following fox tracks
svg.desc: Buggie, the Bugzilla's mascot, dressed up in a Detective's outfit, consisting of a shirt and brown suit, with brown shorts, short brown shoes and a deerstalker hat, bent over with its left hand on its knee, and a loupe in its right hand, looking down at five fox prints arranged in a line. It has a concerned expression on its face.
